The '''Republic Defense Procurement plan''' was a project launched by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] in [[39 BBY/Legends|39 BBY]]. In it, they purchased a number of weapons and [[Starship/Legends|ships]] from [[Republic Sienar Systems/Legends|Republic Sienar Systems]].

